  "lyrics": "Those dark days seem to be trying to find a light but it's for the moment Don't need to rehearse and assess lost thoughts Don't need another verse to explain we should care It won't be easy making it past this line Explain to you all my mistrust, arguing less than dozen I should know that pain comes before the dawn That I'm not here to disperse hate Relate, conquer the past equations without divination Cause it all doesn't last long, no Find that place you belong to I belong with me, belong to my views and my structure of color If I let you in past the braces, past the war, past what love is for Can you not blame, find your sin, show you belong to you Your truth self signed, when you find that place you belong Hold on, no It doesn't last long at all, no If the light reaches you tonight I'm thankful that all I've gone through Can be told again, used as a tool Encapsulate the silver lining, be like cat, it's a dance to live in Life without strife, without judgment, yeah Somewhere you'll be happy, with you Happy in a place to belong to I want to belong to I want to belong with you I belong with me, belong to my views and my structure of color If I let you in past the braces, past the war, past what love is for Can you not blame, find your sin, show you belong to you Your truth self signed, when you find that place you belong Hold on, no It doesn't last long at all, no So now the world has acknowledged your misery No ancient foreign chemistry Just your heart beating next to me and a life with you Equations of understanding, a place to build happy for those Who don't have one A place to sing a song, yeah Baby, a place Where we can Belong Thanks for watching!",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 23.479999542236328,
      "text": "Those dark days seem to be trying to find a light but it's for the moment",
      "start": 16.020000457763672
    },
    {
      "end": 27.719999313354492,
      "text": "Don't need to rehearse and assess lost thoughts",
      "start": 23.799999237060547
    },
    {
      "end": 32.36000061035156,
      "text": "Don't need another verse to explain we should care",
      "start": 27.719999313354492
    },
    {
      "end": 39.279998779296875,
      "text": "It won't be easy making it past this line",
      "start": 32.52000045776367
    },
    {
      "end": 44.36000061035156,
      "text": "Explain to you all my mistrust, arguing less than dozen",
      "start": 39.7599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 48.5,
      "text": "I should know that pain comes before the dawn",
      "start": 44.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 52.34000015258789,
      "text": "That I'm not here to disperse hate",
      "start": 48.5
    },
    {
      "end": 56.52000045776367,
      "text": "Relate, conquer the past equations without divination",
      "start": 52.34000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 60.36000061035156,
      "text": "Cause it all doesn't last long, no",
      "start": 56.52000045776367
    },
    {
      "end": 64.4800033569336,
      "text": "Find that place you belong to",
      "start": 60.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 72,
      "text": "I belong with me, belong to my views and my structure of color",
      "start": 64.4800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 79.5999984741211,
      "text": "If I let you in past the braces, past the war, past what love is for",
      "start": 72
    },
    {
      "end": 84.63999938964844,
      "text": "Can you not blame, find your sin, show you belong to you",
      "start": 79.5999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 88.83999633789062,
      "text": "Your truth self signed, when you find that place you belong",
      "start": 84.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 90.69999694824219,
      "text": "Hold on, no",
      "start": 88.91999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 96.04000091552734,
      "text": "It doesn't last long at all, no",
      "start": 91.62000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 99.91999816894531,
      "text": "If the light reaches you tonight",
      "start": 96.81999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 104.30000305175781,
      "text": "I'm thankful that all I've gone through",
      "start": 100.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 108.9800033569336,
      "text": "Can be told again, used as a tool",
      "start": 104.4000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 115.66000366210938,
      "text": "Encapsulate the silver lining, be like cat, it's a dance to live in",
      "start": 110.16000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 118.37999725341797,
      "text": "Life without strife, without judgment, yeah",
      "start": 115.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 122.4800033569336,
      "text": "Somewhere you'll be happy, with you",
      "start": 118.37999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 128.5399932861328,
      "text": "Happy in a place to belong to",
      "start": 123
    },
    {
      "end": 133.86000061035156,
      "text": "I want to belong to",
      "start": 129.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 142.33999633789062,
      "text": "I want to belong with you",
      "start": 135.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 150.1999969482422,
      "text": "I belong with me, belong to my views and my structure of color",
      "start": 143.75999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 158.02000427246094,
      "text": "If I let you in past the braces, past the war, past what love is for",
      "start": 150.1999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 165,
      "text": "Can you not blame, find your sin, show you belong to you",
      "start": 159.32000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 169.6999969482422,
      "text": "Your truth self signed, when you find that place you belong",
      "start": 165
    },
    {
      "end": 172.02000427246094,
      "text": "Hold on, no",
      "start": 169.6999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 176,
      "text": "It doesn't last long at all, no",
      "start": 172.67999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 179.77999877929688,
      "text": "So now the world has acknowledged your misery",
      "start": 176
    },
    {
      "end": 183.13999938964844,
      "text": "No ancient foreign chemistry",
      "start": 180.1999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 188.3000030517578,
      "text": "Just your heart beating next to me and a life with you",
      "start": 183.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 193.13999938964844,
      "text": "Equations of understanding, a place to build happy for those",
      "start": 188.3000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 195.6199951171875,
      "text": "Who don't have one",
      "start": 193.32000732421875
